## Part 9: Accessibility

WCAG 2.1 AA compliance

---
template: content
---

## Accessibility Validation (v2.0.0)

MDSlides automatically validates presentations:

**Checks performed:**
- **Contrast Ratios** - Text vs background (WCAG 2.1 AA)
- **Alt Text** - All images have descriptions
- **Keyboard Navigation** - Arrow keys, Home, End, Esc work

**Pass/warning modes:**
- Pass: All checks successful
- Warning: Non-blocking issues found (presentation still generated)

---
template: content
---

## Accessibility Configuration

Control accessibility validation:

```bash
# Enable validation (default)
mdslides render deck

# Skip validation
mdslides render deck --skip-accessibility

# Generate JSON report
mdslides render deck --accessibility-report report.json
```

**Configuration:**
```json
{
  "skipAccessibility": false,
  "accessibilityReportPath": "reports/a11y.json"
}
```

